---
title: Mediterranean Spiced Sweet Potato Wrap with Cilantro Raita
description: Start this spring off with a veggie-packed pita! You won't believe how easy it is to make yogurt riata. When it's all done,  dollop the raita on top of the Mediterranean-spiced veg and tuck in!
